Type: Package
Package: mfsusieR
Title: Multi-Modality Multi-Functional Sum of Single Effects Regression
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Date: 2026-04-25
Authors@R: c(
    person("Gao", "Wang", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "wang.gao@columbia.edu"),
    person("William R. P.", "Denault", role = "aut"),
    person("Anjing", "Liu", role = "aut"),
    person("Matthew", "Stephens", role = "aut"))
Description: A multi-modality, multi-functional generalisation of the
    'Sum of Single Effects' (SuSiE) model for variable selection in
    regression with mixtures of functional and univariate responses.
    Built on the 'susieR' backbone, with wavelet-based functional priors
    and a per-(scale, modality) variance structure. Refactor of the
    'mvf.susie.alpha' prototype.
